        <abstract>
            <p>Refers to part of JDH letter on glacial period sent on to Lyell. CD will not yield. Cannot think how JDH attaches so much attention to physicists. Has "come not to care at all for general beliefs without the special facts".</p>
            <p>His health is improved but not so good as JDH supposes.</p>
        </abstract>
